data.name: Fastr
data.description:
As a full-stack engineer, played a pivotal role in shaping a job portal for the UK-based startup using Next.js.

 The platform catered to both job seekers and job creators, significantly reducing tasks around times and promoting independent task management among engineers.

data.name: ArgoGpt
data.description:
Say goodbye to shadow GPT that duplicates and scatters expensive prompt engineering efforts within the company/team. 

 Say hello to efficiency with ArgoGPT - our team-based GPT client that allows admins to centrally create, curate, version and manage prompts, plugins, and content that is seamlessly consumed by all team members.

data.name: ComplianceOn
data.description:
Delivered a complete front-end solution for a security and compliance automation software start-up based in the United States.

 Designed and implemented a sophisticated analytics and report generation service, in addition to creating an integrated in-app marketplace featuring Stripe payment gateway integration.

data.name: Gfacility Webapp
data.description:
Played a pivotal role in three projects from their initial phases encompassing the main web applications and other applications (PWAs), enhancing meeting booking service at the core while facilitating other solutions such as visitors, catering, meeting room, finances, and other management.

 - Designed a real-time event synchronisation service for both Google and Outlook calendars.

 - Contributed to crafting the add-ins for both Google and Outlook calendars, facilitating seamless integration between the main application and external meeting booking providers.

 Key achievements:

 - Helped to save more than 40% on infra cost while stabilising the overall system by moving event syncing to a serverless architecture.

 - Was appreciated for my work and results and thus was offered to join full-time multiple times.

data.name: Room signage
data.description:
Optimize your meeting and conference room management with the smart Gfacility Building Management Solution. 

 Gain real-time control of your meeting and conference room availability status directly from your device. Stay informed about the daily and hourly changes in your facilities bookings and automatically keep the meeting room signage updated for your visitors. Gfacilitate your room signage process to improve your meeting quality, create a stellar visitor experience, and increase your team’s productivity. 

 With the Gfacility Room Signage solution, you have all meeting details and room status updates at your fingertips. Reschedule your meetings easily from your smart device, and simply tap on the signage to begin, end, or extend your meeting. Manage your meeting rooms smartly to ensure exceptional coordination and flawless meeting organization in your company. 

 Have your meeting room availability distinctly signaled through LED lighting and ensure the smooth and error-free signage process required for improving your business productivity. 

 Use our facility management software to make instant bookings from your device in case of unplanned or emergency meetings, or extend your existing booking on the spot with just one tap. This fast, easy, and flexible booking option helps your team respond to unexpected situations and increases their efficiency. 

 Free-up booked meeting rooms no longer in use or upon meeting cancellation and send availability updates to notify room’s live status. Easily keep track of your facility status and effectively modify your schedule as per your business goals.
